      },
      "date": "2012-12-05 19:47:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nSorry, but this commit message doesn't really explain anything.\n\nWhich callbacks? How are they broken? What problem does this cause, and under what cobditions? What is done to fix them?\n\nIt shouldn't be necessary to look at two Jira tickets to understand basic information about what a commit is doing.",
