      "date": "2012-12-07 15:16:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/09e06e52-407c-11e2-a16b-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
